    "name": "Angel Wings: Endless Night",
    "steam_appid": 1714360,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": true,
    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714360/extras/3da96b334869d6d29a43121820edc3fd.avif?t=1730944214\" width=500 height=80 /></span><br>A dark thriller with both comedic and spine-chilling moments, <i>Angel Wings: Endless Night</i> is a love letter to classic survival horror games, brought to life in visual novel form.<br><br>As a spin-off sequel to <i>Angel Wings</i>, <i>Endless Night</i> finds you trapped in a haunted mansion with no means of escape. Using your wits and the help of your unlikely companion, will you find a way to end this eternal darkness?<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714360/extras/eee4985aa436bd4f10adbe5390230c20.avif?t=1730944214\" width=500 height=80 /></span><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>A gripping story written by the original <i>Angel Wings</i> developers, featuring an all-new cast of characters<br></li><li>Fully voice acted dialogue featuring performances from Tiffany Grant, Ed Nash, and others<br></li><li>A choose-your-own-adventure style journey with over 12 possible endings<br></li><li>Bold, striking character designs with multiple alternate outfits</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1714360/extras/a1d044aebd29872fb18e24c6aa4fe328.avif?t=1730944214\" width=500 height=80 /></span><br>Following the reception of the original <i>Angel Wings</i>, the RumR Design team has expanded to include professional UI/UX developers as well as additional story support.<br><br>Fortunate enough to retain our original art, writing, and dev teams, the final result of <i>Endless Night</i> should be a familiar experience to <i>Angel Wings</i> veterans, while still providing a fresh take from a new perspective.",
